 CD 2: Recorded live on stage at the Hirsch Coliseum, Shreveport / Lousianna, on December 15, 1956
  
Press note:
 This 2-disc 7" set celebrates Elvis' legendary 2nd album that quickly outsold his debut album ELVIS PRESLEY. The included 16-page booklet features great photographs taken from a photo session held in February 1956. The album includes every known outtake from the Labor-Day sessions, in addition to CD 2 featuring the historic live concert at Hirsch Coliseum - Youth Center, Louisiana State Fairgrounds on December 15, 1956.
